  "description": "The fold barely bends the waveform — foldAmt at its gentlest, a single layer, high symmetry. Bright but clean, like sunlight through a single sheet of white paper. Slow attack lets the tone breathe before it lands. The simplest possible origami: a single crease, a crane taking shape.",
